# Savia Mobile Android — Infrastructure (.acm)
> hash: sha256:auto | generated: 2026-03-30 | lines: 65

## Network Layer

### BridgeClient
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../network/BridgeClient.kt`
- **Purpose**: OkHttp client configured for Bridge HTTPS (self-signed TLS)
- **Dependencies**: OkHttp, TrustManager (custom for self-signed certs)
- **Base URL**: https://localhost:8922 (configurable)
- **Auth**: Bearer token from AuthManager

### SSE Handler
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../network/SseHandler.kt` (or inline in ChatViewModel)
- **Purpose**: Chunked transfer encoding parser for chat streaming
- **Pattern**: OkHttp EventSource or manual chunked reading

## Auth

### AuthManager
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../auth/AuthManager.kt`
- **Purpose**: Token storage, session persistence, login/logout
- **Storage**: SharedPreferences (encrypted)
- **Session**: Persists across app restarts

## OTA Updates

### UpdateManager
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../UpdateManager.kt`
- **Purpose**: Check and install APK updates from Bridge
- **Endpoints**: Bridge /updates/check, /updates/download
- **Publish**: APK auto-published to ~/.savia/bridge/apk/ and scripts/dist/

## Notifications

### NotificationManager
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../notifications/NotificationManager.kt`
- **Purpose**: Local notifications for approvals, reminders, chat mentions

## DI Modules (Hilt)

### NetworkModule
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../di/NetworkModule.kt`
- **Purpose**: Provides OkHttpClient, BridgeClient as singletons
- **Scope**: @Singleton

### AppModule
- **File**: `app/src/main/kotlin/.../di/AppModule.kt`
- **Purpose**: Provides AuthManager, UpdateManager, SharedPreferences
- **Scope**: @Singleton

## Bridge Endpoints Used

| Endpoint | Method | Used By |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/auth/login` | POST | AuthManager |
| `/auth/me` | GET | AuthManager |
| `/chat` | POST (SSE) | ChatViewModel |
| `/projects` | GET | HomeViewModel |
| `/dashboard` | GET | DashboardViewModel |
| `/backlog` | GET | KanbanScreen |
| `/updates/check` | GET | UpdateManager |
| `/updates/download` | GET | UpdateManager |
